		<english-features>
			<ul>  
				<li> Derby has a small footprint -- about 2.6 megabytes for the base engine and embedded JDBC driver.</li>				  
				<li> Derby is based on the Java, JDBC, and SQL standards.</li>				  
				<li> Derby provides an embedded JDBC driver that lets you embed Derby in any Java-based solution.</li>				  
				<li> Derby also supports the more familiar client/server mode with the Derby Network Client JDBC driver and Derby Network Server</li>				  
				<li> Derby is easy to install, deploy, and use.</li>				
